metadata.name: La Pedrera Serie 1 #177
metadata.description:
This project is inspired from Gaudí's Casa Milà in Barcelona, also known as La Pedrera. 

This is the first part of a 2-part-serie based on La Pedrera.

In this project, which is intentionaly saturated in color, you will recognize an abstract reproduction of the curved floors and windows of La Casa Milà.

The colors are accentued by the flowers disseminated on each floor. 

Main features of this project include:
- Palette: 10 colors,
- Texture: Strong or Soft,
- Noise: True or False,
- Strong Lines: True or False,
- Flower Packing: Mini or Maxi.

In live mode, press [s] to save a 1200 x 1500 (4 DPI) version of the mint.

Thanks a lot to everyone who will mint a token! :)

metadata.name: FRUSTRATIA - TheFEARZ #23
metadata.description:
Don´t have FOMO - FEARZ are here!

THE FEARZ UNIVERSE
A universe of over 10.000 NFTs - unique digital collectibles

There are 5 countries on the FEARZ Planet and one of them is FRUSTRATIA.
In FRUSTRATIA, everything is wet, damp and slimy. :Soul_Consumer_Pepe: 
It is constantly dark and for that reason, all FEARZ here usually react to everything in a disappointed, angry, aggressive, sometimes bitter, demotivated, depressed or even dejected way.🪖 
They always let others feel their disappointment and take out their frustration and related anger on them.

There will be 5 drops, one every two weeks for each country on the FEARZ planet.
(LOST ANGELES, PANIC HILLS, DEPRESSLAND, FRUSTRATIA)

Whoever holds an NFT from each country on Saturday, 10th of Sep, is qualified and receives a SPECIAL AIRDROP!

metadata.name: Migration #95
metadata.description:
"Migration" is a generative work with which I want to ease my worries about the irresponsibility of people towards the planet they live on.
If we migrate, I hope it will be for the purpose of exploring new areas and not because we have destroyed the planet we live on and are now forced to flee.

Created with 100% p5.js code and math.

Hi-res. options:

- press 'i' to save .png with resolution = 1000px x 1000px
- press 't' to save .png with resolution = 2000px x 2000px
- press 's' to save .png with resolution = 6000px x 6000px


@Mutart, July, 2022.
